data.title: Ana Ularu
data.text:
Romanian actress and model

Ana Ularu (born 26 June 1985) is a Romanian actress and model.

Biography

[edit]

She is known for playing the role of Matilda in Outbound[1] and West in Emerald City (2017).[2]
